text: La Roche is a municipality of the district Gruyère in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. == Villages == La Bélvedère, La Berra, La Breiteneyre, La Serbache, Le Tsubel, Le Villaret and Montsofloz. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Municipalities in Gruyère
